# SPLICE Production Readiness Audit - Complete Report

**Date:** January 12, 2026
**Status:** âš ï¸ **NOT READY FOR LAUNCH** - Critical issues require fixes
**Scope:** All UI features, AI modules, JSX bridge, authentication, and core workflows
**Audited Modules:** 8 core modules + JSX bridge + main event flow

---

## Executive Summary

A comprehensive audit of SPLICE identified **18 CRITICAL production blockers** and **27 HIGH-severity issues** across 8 modules. These issues will cause UI freezes, data corruption, authentication failures, and memory exhaustion under production load.

### Critical Findings

| Module | CRITICAL Issues | HIGH Issues | Risk Level |
|--------|----------------|-------------|------------|
| **JSX Bridge** | 1 | 0 | ğŸ”´ EXTREME |
| **Music Generation** | 5 | 12 | ğŸ”´ EXTREME |
| **Main.js/runDetection** | 2 | 3 | ğŸ”´ CRITICAL |
| **Animated Captions** | 3 | 5 | ğŸ”´ CRITICAL |
| **Multitrack Editing** | 3 | 5 | ğŸŸ  HIGH |
| **Social Reframe** | 3 | 2 | ğŸŸ  HIGH |
