| **Text Editor** | 0 | 2 | ğŸŸ¡ MEDIUM |
| **TOTAL** | **18** | **27** | ğŸ”´ **CRITICAL** |

### Top 5 Production Blockers (Must Fix Before Launch)

1. **JSX Bridge Timeout Bug** - UI freezes indefinitely if Premiere Pro hangs (affects ALL features)
2. **Music Polling Memory Leak** - Server overload + browser crash after 100 rapid operations
3. **Animated Captions Timeline Loop** - 15+ second UI freeze when applying 100+ captions
4. **Main.js Export Timeout** - No timeout on audio export causes permanent UI freeze
5. **Multitrack Race Condition** - Double operations corrupt analysis state

