### 4. Animated Captions (animatedCaptions.js) â›” SEVERITY: CRITICAL

**Location:** `splice-cep/panel/js/animatedCaptions.js`

#### CRITICAL #1: Timeline Loop Blocks UI (Lines 525-528)

**Impact:** 15+ second UI freeze for 100 captions

**Root Cause:**
```javascript
for (const caption of animatedCaptionsState.captions) {
    await jsx.call('createMarker', caption.start, caption.text, ...);
}
// 100 captions Ã— 150ms = 15 seconds frozen UI!
```

**Fix:** Batch processing
```javascript
const BATCH_SIZE = 10;
for (let i = 0; i < captions.length; i += BATCH_SIZE) {
    const batch = captions.slice(i, i + BATCH_SIZE);
    await Promise.all(batch.map(caption =>
        jsx.call('createMarker', caption.start, caption.text, ...)
    ));
    showCaptionStatus(`Applying... (${i}/${captions.length})`);
    await new Promise(r => setTimeout(r, 0)); // Yield to UI
}
```

**Fix Estimate:** 2 hours

---

#### CRITICAL #2: Template Gallery Blocking (Lines 202-229)

**Impact:** Panel initialization delay

**Fix:** Lazy loading + virtualization

**Fix Estimate:** 2 hours

---

#### CRITICAL #3: Preview Not Debounced (Line 347)

**Impact:** Layout thrashing on rapid template changes

**Fix:** Add debounce (150ms)

**Fix Estimate:** 30 minutes

---

**Total Animated Captions Fix Time:** ~5 hours
**Priority:** Fix before launch (marquee AI feature)

