### 8. Text Editor (textEditor.js) ğŸŸ¡ SEVERITY: MEDIUM

**Location:** `splice-cep/panel/js/textEditor.js`

#### HIGH #1: Unbounded Undo Memory Leak (Lines 280-290)

**Impact:** 3MB+ per 50 keystrokes with large transcripts

**Fix:** Delta-based undo (store only changes)

**Fix Estimate:** 3 hours

